snippet.title: WHAT THE HEALTH? Rachele Brooke Smith and Neurohacker Interview (must watch video)
snippet.description:
What if everything you thought you knew about what was healthy for you was wrong? 

In this interview Rachele Brooke Smith interviews Daniel Schmachtenberger, creator of Neuohacker.com, all about the truth and reality behind real health and wellness. 

Question everything and always be on a constant quest for your health... real lasting health and well being, not just what main stream health tells you.
